This open source software is intended to provide ABIs for the
Accessible Technologies (ATs) and desktops to build with so that
the TTS Runtime will work.

AUTHORS		maintainers of this program
ChangeLog	list of all changes made to program source files
CONTRIBUTE	contribution agreement
COPYING		license of this program
INSTALL		instructions how to build and install this program
LICENSE		end-user agreement
NEWS		list of releases worth mentioning
README		this file

The upstream source code is maintained at: 

	http://sourceforge.net/projects/ibmtts-sdk/

Copyrighted developer documentation for IBM TTS can be obtained at:

	http://www.wizzardsoftware.com/docs/tts.pdf

